site.laube.modelinterface

インタフェース ActivityModelInterface

  • 既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    ActivityModel, CommonActivityModel, IndividualActivityModel, SpecialActivityModel

    public interface ActivityModelInterface
    ModelInterface is the class of the order to ensure that there is no reliance on the control class even if the change is DataBase.
    to manage the activities master model interface.
    when you use this framework be sure to implement this interface.
    導入されたバージョン:
    Class deprecated in Release 1.0.0
    バージョン:
    1.0.0
    作成者:
    Ryuta Miki of Pocket Soft Co.,Ltd
